cat ~/.config/cocapn/github-pat

# SuperInstance credentials
cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/.credentials/github-pat.txt
```

**PURPOSE:** Verify I can push to repos.

**CHECKLIST:**
- [ ] Fleet knowledge PAT: [exists / readable / correct]
- [ ] SuperInstance PAT: [exists / readable / correct]

**IF MISSING:** Request new PAT from Casey, store in correct location

