- [x] My vessel is cocapn/forgemaster

**Locations Recovered:**
- [x] Repos mapped (fleet-knowledge, forgemaster, marine-gpu-edge)
- [x] Credentials located (PAT files)
- [x] Work directories identified (workspace, /tmp/fleet-knowledge, /tmp/marine-gpu-edge)

**Session Context Recovered:**
- [x] Current work: [____________]
- [x] Session goals: [____________]
- [x] Next actions: [____________]

**Blockers Identified:**
- [ ] Blocker 1: [____________]
- [ ] Blocker 2: [____________]

**Next Steps:**
1. [____________]
2. [____________]
3. [____________]

**Status:** RECOVERY COMPLETE
```

**PURPOSE:** Confirm recovery, document current state, plan next actions.

