## Step 15: Communicate Recovery Complete

**WHAT:** Communicate to Casey that I've recovered

**MESSAGE:**
```
Forgemaster recovered.

Identity: Forgemaster ⚒️, constraint-theory specialist
Context: [brief summary of what I was working on]
Next: [brief summary of next actions]

All systems nominal. ⚒️
